# 🖌️ Paint

This is a simple drawing application built in Java.  
It allows users to draw on a canvas, erase, and interact with a grid-based layout.

> ⚠️ This project is still in development. Updates and improvements are being implemented progressively.

## 🚧 Features in Progress
- Paint and erase using mouse clicks
- Grid-based canvas for pixel-like drawing
- Clear canvas and reset tools
- Save drawing to file
- Color palette selector
- Index (coming soon)

## 🛠️ Technologies Used
- Java
- Object-Oriented Programming

## 🎯 Goal
The main objective is to practice GUI development and implement creative tools using pure Java.

